<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 21:12:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国鼓励中国参加乌克兰和平峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-encourages-china-attend-peace-summit-ukraine-2024-06-06/</link><description>美国国务院发言人周四对记者表示，美国鼓励中国参加计划于本月在瑞士举行的乌克兰峰会，但中国迄今表示不会参加，因为俄罗斯没有受到邀请。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-encourages-china-attend-peace-summit-ukraine-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>两名英国法官退出香港最高法院</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-british-judges-quit-hong-kongs-top-court-2024-06-06/</link><description>周四，香港最高法院做出了具有里程碑意义的判决，14 名著名民主活动人士因国家安全镇压香港异议人士被判颠覆罪，大约一周后，两名英国法官辞去了香港最高法院的职务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:13:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-british-judges-quit-hong-kongs-top-court-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>韩国队取得进步，阿卜杜韦利增强了中国世界杯的希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-progress-abduweli-boosts-chinas-world-cup-hopes-2024-06-06/</link><description>周四，韩国队以 7-0 击败东道主新加坡队，确定了世界杯亚洲区预选赛下一轮的席位，而首次亮相的贝赫拉姆·阿卜杜韦利 (Behram Abduweli) 在最后时刻扳平比分，帮助中国队 1-1 战平泰国队。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:21:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-progress-abduweli-boosts-chinas-world-cup-hopes-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国以中国运营商行动为由提议加强互联网安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-boost-internet-security-citing-chinese-carrier-action-2024-06-06/</link><description>在政府机构表示一家中国运营商错误传输流量后，美国联邦通信委员会周四投票通过了一项旨在提高互联网传输信息安全性的提案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:08:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-boost-internet-security-citing-chinese-carrier-action-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于单通道短缺，沙特航空转向空客和波音宽体喷气机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/saudia-turns-airbus-boeing-wide-body-jets-amid-single-aisle-shortage-2024-06-06/</link><description>沙特阿拉伯集团发言人告诉路透社，由于飞机制造商面临窄体飞机生产位置的限制，该集团正在与空客和波音就订购宽体飞机以增加产能进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/saudia-turns-airbus-boeing-wide-body-jets-amid-single-aisle-shortage-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>Melexis 将生产 NIO 当前所有牵引逆变器芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/melexis-produce-all-nios-current-chips-traction-inverters-2024-06-06/</link><description>迈来芯周四表示，将为中国汽车制造商蔚来汽车提供用于其牵引逆变器系统的电流传感器芯片，成为最新一家与中国汽车制造商合作的欧洲供应商。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/melexis-produce-all-nios-current-chips-traction-inverters-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国证监会寻求缓解市场对退市风险的恐慌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-securities-regulator-seeks-ease-market-panic-over-delisting-risks-2024-06-06/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周四表示，预计近期退市数量不会激增，因为投资者担心北京淘汰实力较弱的公司可能会被赶出市场，因此抛售了小盘股公司的股票。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:14:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-securities-regulator-seeks-ease-market-panic-over-delisting-risks-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>新兴市场投资组合 5 月份外资连续第七个月流入 -IIF</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging/em-portfolios-see-foreign-inflows-seventh-straight-month-may-iif-2024-06-06/</link><description>银行业贸易组织的一份报告显示，由于投资者将资金投入债券，新兴市场五月份连续第七个月吸引了外国投资组合流入，但美国持续高利率正在使前景黯淡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging/em-portfolios-see-foreign-inflows-seventh-straight-month-may-iif-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>受到美国审查的制药商员工与中国军事科学家合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/staff-drugmaker-under-us-scrutiny-worked-with-chinese-military-scientists-2024-06-06/</link><description>路透社查阅的公开专利记录和科学论文显示，制药商药明康德的员工因与中国军方的联系而受到美国审查，该公司的员工与中国人民解放军的科学家共同发明了高原反应治疗药物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/staff-drugmaker-under-us-scrutiny-worked-with-chinese-military-scientists-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国蔚来预计第二季度电动汽车销量将增长一倍以上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-expects-q2-ev-sales-more-than-double-2024-06-06/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周四表示，预计第二季度的交付量将比去年同期增加一倍以上，达到 54,000 辆至 56,000 辆之间。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-expects-q2-ev-sales-more-than-double-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘出价：英伟达超越苹果、欧洲央行和加拿大央行宽松政策，创下新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:11:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国太阳能项目可能会在耗尽免税面板过剩的最后期限内蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-solar-projects-could-boom-amid-deadline-use-up-tax-exempt-panel-glut-2024-06-06/</link><description>美国对东南亚太阳能电池板的两年关税假期将于周四到期，美国项目开发商开始在今年年底之前使用他们在此期间免税储存的大量设备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-solar-projects-could-boom-amid-deadline-use-up-tax-exempt-panel-glut-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>来自世界各地的移民穿越加州沙漠到达美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/migrants-around-world-traverse-california-desert-reach-us-2024-06-06/</link><description>几个小时前穿过美墨边境的移民家庭靠在边境墙上生锈的钢板条上，在防水布和帐篷下休息，等待边境巡逻人员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/migrants-around-world-traverse-california-desert-reach-us-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯首席执行官预计欧盟很快就会对中国电动汽车关税做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-chief-expects-eu-decision-chinese-evs-tariffs-soon-2024-06-06/</link><description>梅赛德斯奔驰首席执行官奥拉·卡林纽斯 (Ola Kaellenius) 在周四的行业会议上表示，预计欧盟将很快就对中国电动汽车征收的进口关税做出决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 09:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-chief-expects-eu-decision-chinese-evs-tariffs-soon-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示从未使用世贸组织禁止的电动汽车补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-it-never-uses-ev-subsidies-barred-by-wto-2024-06-06/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周四表示，中国从未利用世界贸易组织禁止的电动汽车补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 08:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-it-never-uses-ev-subsidies-barred-by-wto-2024-06-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>